      "comment": "STAR VISION (4) is stepping out for the first time. By Always B Miki and hails from the Emma Stewart stable. Looks to have some ability based on a recent trial win. Will be right there at the business end. COMINSKI LEIS (7) finished a nose from the winner in second at this track over 1609m last start at his first career run. Will need a bit of luck negotiating a very wide starting position. His last-start form is good enough to take out a race like this. ANGELIC (1) lines up for the first time. By Captaintreacherous and hails from the Tammy Langley stable. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Showed some ability when a minor placegetter in a recent trial. Capable of taking this out. VOODOO RANGER NZ (2) is in the mix following a sixth at his most recent appearance over 1609m at this track.",
